-- Peacocks May Sell Bonmarche Chain This Week, Times Reports
-- B y   M i c h a e l   P a t t e r s o n
-- 2012-01-15T09:47:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-15/peacocks-may-sell-bonmarche-chain-this-week-times-reports.html
U.K. budget retailer Peacocks may
sell its Bonmarche womens-wear chain this week, the Sunday Times
reported, without saying where it got the information.  Sun European Partners, a turnaround specialist, is the
leading bidder for Bonmarche, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
